(27, 4, 3, '<p>Ruth:Â Hey, did you catch any of the Olympic events last night?</p>\n<p><br>Tian:Â Yeah, I watched the gymnastics competition. It was insane!</p>\n<p><br>Ruth: Right? The level of skill and precision is mind-blowing. I can\'t believe what those athletes can do.</p>\n<p><br>Tian:Â I know, and the atmosphere is just on another level during the Olympics. The whole world comes together to celebrate sports.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth:Â Exactly! It\'s not just about the competition; it\'s a celebration of human achievement. The opening ceremony was spectacular.</p>\n<p><br>Tian: The unity and diversity on display during the Parade of Nations-it gives you goosebumps.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth:Â And hearing the national anthems when athletes win gold-it\'s emotional. You can see how much it means to them.</p>\n<p><br>Tian: The stories of perseverance and dedication behind each athlete add another layer of depth to the experience.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth: Totally. I was watching swimming, and the underdog who came out of nowhere to win-it\'s like a real-life fairy tale.</p>\n<p><br>Tian: The Olympic spirit is contagious. It makes you want to push yourself to achieve more, even if it\'s just in your own little world.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth: Plus, the sportsmanship is incredible. Competitors hug each other after a tough race, showing respect-it\'s a beautiful aspect of the games.</p>\n<p><br>Tian:Â And you can\'t forget the breathtaking moments, like when an athlete breaks a world record. It\'s history in the making.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth: Right, it\'s like witnessing greatness unfold before your eyes. Makes you proud to be part of the global audience.</p>\n<p><br>Tian:Â Couldn\'t agree more. The Olympics are a celebration of human potential and the power of sport to bring people together.</p>\n<p><br>Ruth: Can\'t wait for the next event. The excitement and sense of unity during the Olympics are truly unmatched.</p>\n<p>Â </p>\n<p>How do the national anthems during the medal ceremony contribute to the emotional aspect of the Olympics, according to Ruth?</p>', NULL, 'pilihan_ganda', 'aktif', 25.71, '2025-09-13 14:54:42', '2025-09-14 18:46:45'),
